    "name": "Unpatterned Cut",
    "steam_appid": 3316430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpatterned Cut 是一款令人上瘾的动作反射游戏，带来了前所未有的体验。在未来风格的环境中与敌人战斗，突破你的极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧集逻辑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不觉得重复的节奏反射游戏很无聊吗？你不再需要记住特定的模式来完成关卡。Unpatterned Cut 为你提供了独特的体验，即使在同一个关卡中，每次重试也会有不同的模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>章节</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏共包含 5 个章节和 16 个关卡。每个章节都有与前一章节不同的特点。例如，如果你成功通过了第一章，那么在第二章中会出现带有护甲的敌人，你需要先破坏他们的护甲才能进行攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还有一个简短的故事模式，你需要做出选择并解释自己为何进入了模拟之中。<strong>你不必玩故事模式也可以进行关卡挑战。</strong></p>",
